A Sandstone Passageway
An eery dark sandstone passageway. To your South you can see outside to the entrance to the maze. To your North you can see a large room. The chute downwards lies open.
The light from the lantern allows you to easily detect and avoid a wooden downwards chute when it is revealed  in the middle of the passageway by an opening trapdoor.
